knowledgeGraph.title: Olive View-UCLA Medical Center
knowledgeGraph.description: Olive View–UCLA Medical Center is a hospital, funded by Los Angeles County, located in the Sylmar neighborhood of Los Angeles, California. It is one of the primary healthcare delivery systems in the north San Fernando Valley, serving the area's large working-class population.
